name: Spotify Wrapped 2021
description:
We’re Example, 2 designers from the Netherlands. Being big music enthausiasts, we set ourself the challenge to ‘’unwrap’’ this years’ Spotify Wrapped. All the visuals, components and everything else that comes with it.


Keep in mind that we did not design the Wrapped campaign, or had anything to do with the project.


Feel free to play around with the file, add yourself as top artist or brag about your 1 million minutes of playtime!


Follow us for more design, unwrapped.
